The Movie Database (TMDB) API

This product uses the TMDB API but is not endorsed or certified by TMDB.

Terms of Use: https://www.themoviedb.org/terms-of-use
API Terms: https://www.themoviedb.org/documentation/api/terms-of-use

TMDB API Key Required:
To use this application, you must obtain your own TMDB API key:
1. Create an account at https://www.themoviedb.org/
2. Request an API key at https://www.themoviedb.org/settings/api
3. Add your API key to config.json (see config.example.json)

By using the TMDB API, you agree to comply with TMDB's Terms of Use.

